        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I want to tell you of an instance of long memory in a horse. I have just driven my pony down from London here, and though she has not been here for eight years, she remembered her way quite well, and made a bolt for the stables where I used to keep her.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>
        
        
        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year range is conjectured from the assumption that the letter was inspired by CD’s work on the mental powers of animals, published in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> in 1871. CD died in April 1882.</note>
                <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD had discussed the instinctive behaviours and mental powers of animals, including horses, in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref>1: 34–106. </note>
        </div>
    
